005package edu.wpi.first.apriltag;
006
007public enum AprilTagFields {
008  k2022RapidReact("2022-rapidreact.json");
009
010  public static final String kBaseResourceDir = "/edu/wpi/first/apriltag/";
011
012  /** Alias to the current game. */
013  public static final AprilTagFields kDefaultField = k2022RapidReact;
014
015  public final String m_resourceFile;
016
017  AprilTagFields(String resourceFile) {
018    m_resourceFile = kBaseResourceDir + resourceFile;
019  }
020}
